posts.subject: Vehicle air conditioning
posts.body: My Honda Pilots air conditioner is in the cahoots and works every other time I drive! Does anyone know anyone reputable to fix it? We’d prefer not to go to a Honda dealership to pay an arm and a leg!

comments.body:
Not sure if Mike at Hampton Cove Auto Service does AC work, but I'd check with him first. Honest guy. Taken my Jeep there a couple of times and he's always done me right.

If you or someone in your family has access to the Arsenal, the MWR Auto Shop there is awesome. There's no where cheaper in town, and they do good work
We just got ours fixed at Prestige Automotive on the Parkway. Pretty reasonable and good work too. Unfortunately air conditioning work is expensive!

posts.subject: Diesel Mechanic
posts.body: We are looking for recommendations, other than the VW dealership, to do some work on our diesel Volkswagen. Does anyone have someone here in Huntsville that is dependable and reasonable?

comments.body: We have gone over to the the VW in Florence! Cheaper, ultra friendly , and the job is done right!
Maybe Johnson Foreign Auto?

posts.subject: Hampton Cove Auto
posts.body: We have been in Hampton Cove for 12 years and have always used HC Automotive for all our car repairs. They are honest, reasonable, dependable and friendly people to do business with. Highly recommend!

posts.subject: AC Car Repair
posts.body: Does anyone have a reputable car repair place that you could recommend? We have an older 4Runner in need of AC repair.

comments.body: There is no doubt about it. Hampton Cove Auto, recommended many, many times on this site. Mike (the owner) is the most honest mechanic/owner I've ever experienced. HC Auto is on 431 near Arbys. You will become a customer for as long as you live here.

responses.body: Thank you! You know we are and always will be here for you.

posts.subject: Auto Mechanic
posts.body: Can anyone recommend a trustworthy mechanic in the area that won't overcharge me like the dealership will? I have an oil leak on my 2008 Yukon Denali that I need to get fixed ASAP. Thanks in advance.

comments.body:
Express Oil on Drake Ave. across from Dillard’s Parkway Place Mall. 

They are reasonable and have very good mechanics. We have used them for a few years after being referred by a family. In fact, my son took his 2007 Tahoe there this morning to have them troubleshoot an issue and give him an estimate for repair.
YES AUTOMOTIVE only place to go, quick, reasonable prices, Gary is the owner, 35 years of experience

posts.subject: Need a mechanic
posts.body: Any recommendations on this side of the mountain or in Huntsville? Have a vehicle w heater core problems. Thanks!

comments.body: Anderson Motor Company on South Parkway have been great to me
My husband can help. He’s very mechanically inclined and has worked as a mechanic. We live in magnolia park and he can help you out for a good price. Message for his number if you’re interested!
